<p>
  <%= @user.name %>,
</p>

<p>
  <%= @from_user.name %> has requested that you change your password at
  <%= ActionMailer::Base.default_url_options[:host] %>. You can do so by
  visiting: <%= link_to new_user_password_url, new_user_password_url %>
</p>

<p>
  From there, enter your email address (<%= @user.email %>) and press the
  button labeled: <%= t("devise.passwords.new.send_me_reset_password_instructions", default: "Send me reset password instructions") %>
</p>

<p>
  You will then receive another email with a link that will allow you to reset
  your password.
</p>
